</subSubSection>
<subSubSection lastPageId="11" lastPageNumber="12" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1437,152,1260]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,330,1157,1183]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Discussion</emphasis>
:— 
<taxonomicName authorityName="W. T. Wang, Y. G. Wei &amp; A. K. Monro" authorityYear="2011" box="[367,540,1157,1182]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Urticaceae" genus="Elatostema" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="lui">
<emphasis box="[367,540,1157,1182]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Elatostema lui</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is most similar to 
<taxonomicName authority="Wang (1988)" authorityName="Wang" authorityYear="1988" box="[772,1174,1157,1183]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Urticaceae" genus="Elatostema" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="platyceras">
<emphasis box="[772,1035,1157,1182]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Elatostema platyceras</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Wang, W. T." box="[1043,1174,1157,1183]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" pagination="343 - 348" refId="ref10616" refString="Wang, W. T. (1988) Notulae de Elatostemate Yunanensi. Acta Botanica Yunnanica 10: 343 - 348." type="journal article" year="1988">Wang (1988)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
from which it can be distinguished based on stem, leaf and staminate inflorescence and flower morphology as summarised in the table below:
</paragraph>
